body:
For those who encounter the same problem, it's because I forked the bsc testnet like this in my configuration:
```
networks: {
  hardhat: {
    forking: {
      url: "https://bsc-testnet.public.blastapi.io",
    },
  },
},
```

Just remove these configuration and it will work

Sorry for the mistake

Have a good day ;)
